Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.55,0:00:09.65,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Noel?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.80,0:00:11.51,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.69,0:00:12.60,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.17,0:00:15.23,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Noel!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.26,0:00:18.52,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.79,0:00:22.83,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Noel!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.41,0:00:23.87,phone,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Koharu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.75,0:00:29.09,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Noel!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.18,0:00:31.69,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Noel!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.22,0:02:09.90,sora-ep-title,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(489,396)}Where Wishes Go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.70,0:02:06.68,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.00,0:02:08.00,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Noel!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.58,0:02:10.80,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.36,0:02:11.94,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.92,0:02:16.10,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.08,0:02:20.32,sora-flashback,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Things get bad when I'm \Nfar from the saucer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.23,0:02:23.55,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,You said you'd be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.16,0:02:26.69,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.02,0:02:29.11,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me, what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.28,0:02:31.50,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,How do I save you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.97,0:02:35.13,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Take me where I can see the saucer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.42,0:02:36.59,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,The saucer?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.79,0:02:37.16,sora-internal-top,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.59,0:02:38.11,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Should we go back to town?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.30,0:02:39.80,sora-internal-top,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Is Noel there? What about the saucer?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.33,0:02:40.41,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Koharu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.41,0:02:41.51,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I'll explain later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.51,0:02:46.19,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on, Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.58,0:02:49.77,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.92,0:02:52.30,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, you came by car today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.48,0:02:52.76,sora-main-top,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.53,0:02:53.77,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Help, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.34,0:02:56.36,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, he's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.40,0:02:57.78,sora-main-top,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Shione?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.76,0:03:06.29,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.60,0:03:08.94,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Noel!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.30,0:03:18.57,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.96,0:03:21.30,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,No. I can't find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.45,0:03:23.39,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they aren't at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.90,0:03:25.04,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.21,0:03:27.02,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,If only I'd paid more attention...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.88,0:03:28.91,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Souta!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.91,0:03:30.83,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make that face.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.00,0:03:33.19,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they went on home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.03,0:03:35.65,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.92,0:03:37.64,sora-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.35,0:03:40.99,sora-flashback,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see the saucer from afar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.38,0:03:45.70,sora-flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,How would you ever \Nleave the town, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.94,0:03:48.76,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,She's fine, I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.50,0:03:55.50,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,She found Noel-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.75,0:03:57.79,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.77,0:04:02.26,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,But something didn't seem \Nright over the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.65,0:04:04.91,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.56,0:04:06.65,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,We're almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.80,0:04:08.20,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there, Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.27,0:04:11.27,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure we just need to bring her home?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.27,0:04:12.48,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.84,0:04:31.84,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You should call if you're worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.00,0:04:35.08,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I think Nonoka will call \Nme when things settle down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.33,0:04:36.83,phone2,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka \N {\fs14}Incoming Call
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.53,0:04:39.59,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka, how's Noel-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.07,0:04:40.99,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.46,0:04:42.62,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.36,0:04:45.24,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,So she's okay, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.74,0:04:47.09,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.60,0:04:54.79,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.79,0:05:03.53,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,You were watching over me so my \Nwish would come true, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.66,0:05:11.66,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,So that we can always keep smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.18,0:05:22.32,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you were by my side
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.74,0:05:25.34,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,that I could have my \Nprecious wish again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:34.15,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.44,0:05:44.54,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.40,0:05:47.65,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Have these with Noel-chan, \Nif you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.40,0:05:47.65,saucer cakes,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Saucer Rice Cakes
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.01,0:05:49.07,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,These, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.37,0:05:51.05,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,This'll make her better.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.09,0:05:55.20,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.10,0:06:00.00,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I was so shocked when I \Nheard that she collapsed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.40,0:06:03.01,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Don't freak us out, shorty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.20,0:06:05.87,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness. Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.19,0:06:16.77,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.16,0:06:20.10,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka, I'm leaving you \Nto take care of Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.30,0:06:23.77,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, I'd like to be \Nthere all night with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.54,0:06:25.36,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.36,0:06:30.17,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm sure Shione really wanted \Nto come to the Hokubi Festival, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.33,0:06:32.00,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Something must have come up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.23,0:06:34.06,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I think so, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.64,0:06:35.78,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for today,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.17,0:06:37.18,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.76,0:06:41.37,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka, what happened to Noel-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.03,0:06:46.30,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,She probably got exhausted \Nat the Hokubi Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.77,0:06:49.22,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried about Noel, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.22,0:06:50.25,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Souta?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.41,0:06:51.88,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,If you know something...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.30,0:06:58.27,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Noel can't leave this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.26,0:07:00.69,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,That's why she collapsed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.69,0:07:03.44,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.20,0:07:07.57,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Noel is the saucer that we called
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.86,0:07:09.82,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,seven years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.73,0:07:16.58,sora-flashback,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Saucer-san, Saucer-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.58,0:07:17.87,sora-flashback,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Please grant my wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.87,0:07:18.78,sora-flashback,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,My wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.78,0:07:19.55,sora-flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,My wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.55,0:07:20.46,sora-flashback,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,My wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.04,0:07:22.88,sora-flashback,All,0000,0000,0000,,Please grant our wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.49,0:07:25.71,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Noel is the saucer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.33,0:07:29.10,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,She's trying to grant \Nthat wish from way back?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.42,0:07:31.83,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Koharu, Souta,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.98,0:07:35.72,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,how are you both convinced \Nthat she's the saucer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.72,0:07:38.10,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,How could that be Noel?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.37,0:07:42.23,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I made Noel help get rid of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.16,0:07:47.57,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Noel was happy that she was giving \Nyou help when you needed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.11,0:07:50.24,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Because she's a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.35,0:07:53.99,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that's what Noel would say.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.90,0:07:57.33,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.72,0:07:59.26,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.41,0:08:01.85,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Noel is the saucer, \Nand she's our friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.00,0:08:04.50,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so nothing's changed, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.35,0:08:06.43,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.94,0:08:28.59,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Soft.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.65,0:08:32.92,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.09,0:08:33.94,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.47,0:08:37.24,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Noel!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.68,0:08:38.87,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.94,0:08:41.00,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Noel!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.16,0:08:43.70,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Nonoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.70,0:08:45.12,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.75,0:08:47.38,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I was so worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.66,0:08:48.69,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone else was, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.43,0:08:50.67,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.84,0:08:52.13,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,About me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.98,0:08:55.77,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka, where's Shione?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.77,0:08:57.77,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Did you smile together?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.82,0:09:02.99,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about us for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.41,0:09:04.88,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.66,0:09:17.41,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.32,0:09:19.71,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.90,0:09:23.05,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,It's not your fault, Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.74,0:09:30.29,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.76,0:09:35.42,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.88,0:09:39.19,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Smile with Shione again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.02,0:09:51.94,sora-flashback,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.94,0:09:54.94,sora-flashback,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,You were back to being friends again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.50,0:09:58.54,sora-flashback,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:10:00.24,sora-flashback,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.24,0:10:02.03,sora-flashback,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,When I talked to her,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.03,0:10:05.70,sora-flashback,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,she said she's happy when \Nshe can smile with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.48,0:10:09.96,sora-flashback,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,What did I do wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.19,0:10:11.97,sora-flashback,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Is it because I ate rice omelet?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.97,0:10:13.92,sora-flashback,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Or because I jumped into \Nthe hot spring bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.08,0:10:15.76,sora-flashback,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Because I passed on a message?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.92,0:10:17.72,sora-flashback,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Because you gave me tickets?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.49,0:10:21.72,sora-flashback,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'll disappear \Nif your wish comes true?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.46,0:11:10.54,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.60,0:11:13.11,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Yuzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.66,0:11:14.92,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,You seem down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.07,0:11:17.78,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen to Noel?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.27,0:11:20.35,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.50,0:11:22.05,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,That's good, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.30,0:11:25.90,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hide anything about \Nher from us, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.16,0:11:27.04,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.29,0:11:29.96,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka, the telescope!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.75,0:11:39.13,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.13,0:11:39.96,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.96,0:11:41.54,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Souta.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.69,0:11:42.70,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,And Yuzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.31,0:11:44.94,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,You scared me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.42,0:11:49.12,sora-flashback,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I brought rice cakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.58,0:11:54.43,sora-flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Koharu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.16,0:11:56.85,sora-flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Souta.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.85,0:11:58.32,sora-flashback,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,What about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.52,0:11:59.57,sora-flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,You, too, Yuzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.61,0:12:02.07,sora-flashback,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Good, you're all here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.96,0:12:04.84,sora-flashback,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone I want you to meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.40,0:12:09.79,sora-flashback,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.56,0:12:12.46,sora-flashback,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Togawa Shione.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.81,0:12:15.96,sora-flashback,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Shione is
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.16,0:12:18.96,sora-flashback,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,my precious
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.37,0:12:21.45,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.52,0:12:45.58,sora-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I can finally go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.07,0:12:50.19,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.54,0:12:53.16,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,About Togawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.56,0:12:55.25,sora-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, about her transfer?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.12,0:12:58.42,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Transfer?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.27,0:13:00.48,sora-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,No?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.57,0:13:02.92,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.43,0:13:07.18,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.77,0:13:09.18,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.50,0:13:11.83,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,She's a precious friend, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.98,0:13:14.22,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take the telescope home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.47,0:13:16.12,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Come to the store later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.12,0:13:18.69,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be the one carrying it, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.65,0:13:21.64,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.79,0:13:22.69,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.98,0:13:38.63,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Shione!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.13,0:13:40.17,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.17,0:13:41.92,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Let me talk to you once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.09,0:13:44.38,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want us to part like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.77,0:13:47.28,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I heard from Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.88,0:13:50.72,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Once our wish comes true, Noel...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.53,0:13:57.64,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Shione.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.84,0:14:01.65,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true you're moving?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.98,0:14:04.11,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just going to be \Nliving at my dad's.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.40,0:14:06.90,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Is that for Noel?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.32,0:14:11.16,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,It is, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.66,0:14:14.40,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,What does it matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.88,0:14:23.69,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I hope we can all smile forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.18,0:14:28.36,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I love all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.63,0:14:30.68,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to lose you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.68,0:14:36.31,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,So let's think about \Nwhat we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.70,0:14:37.85,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.29,0:14:40.23,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.62,0:14:44.40,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not as attached \Nto the observatory as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.70,0:14:46.23,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,I just went because you invited me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.02,0:14:49.41,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,I leave, and Noel stays.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.63,0:14:51.40,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,What's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.31,0:14:56.41,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.56,0:14:57.60,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.94,0:15:05.85,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.22,0:15:08.51,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,I love all of you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.67,0:15:12.25,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,What am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.61,0:15:17.42,sora-flashback,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Shione is my precious friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.78,0:15:20.73,sora-flashback,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,She's my friend, too, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.41,0:15:23.02,sora-flashback,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,No fair, Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.02,0:15:24.28,sora-flashback,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.49,0:15:25.88,sora-flashback,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.74,0:15:28.83,sora-flashback,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.16,0:15:33.44,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.07,0:15:51.64,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.55,0:15:54.59,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.96,0:15:56.18,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Do you feel okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.18,0:15:57.12,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.12,0:15:58.06,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,See.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.95,0:16:00.11,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.30,0:16:01.43,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.01,0:16:06.94,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I really want to grant your wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.54,0:16:12.54,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Is that because we called \Nyou to this town?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.72,0:16:14.95,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,At first, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.12,0:16:16.20,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,At first?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.52,0:16:19.70,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I realized after I watched you guys
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.28,0:16:25.42,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,that your wish is really, \Nreally beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.81,0:16:30.84,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,That you can smile, \Nand always be connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.31,0:16:34.47,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,That your hearts would \Nalways be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.65,0:16:37.10,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,That's such a beautiful thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.60,0:16:41.68,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,So I want to see you all smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.40,0:16:47.40,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.34,0:16:51.79,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,But that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.40,0:16:54.40,Closed,Text,0000,0000,0000,,We're closed for the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.15,0:16:58.36,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You're in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.51,0:17:00.27,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Go home if you're \Nnot doing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.27,0:17:01.53,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.53,0:17:03.20,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm waiting for Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.37,0:17:04.66,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,That's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.90,0:17:07.21,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I want to ask about Shione.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.41,0:17:10.09,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Something's wrong with \Nher these days, I swear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.27,0:17:17.78,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Shione!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.32,0:17:20.57,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Shione.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.93,0:17:22.35,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.81,0:17:24.88,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.04,0:17:26.97,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Go back to Nonoka's.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.83,0:17:30.22,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Shione?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.60,0:17:35.87,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, we're closed for...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.20,0:17:37.26,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Shione?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.26,0:17:37.86,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.86,0:17:40.30,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,You! Where were you all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.30,0:17:41.86,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,We were worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.86,0:17:43.22,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.39,0:17:44.54,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Nonoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.94,0:17:47.87,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.53,0:17:49.88,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,About Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.98,0:17:57.04,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I have to get the telescope.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.84,0:18:04.02,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Mom,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.84,0:18:07.46,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,what am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.30,0:18:16.46,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.36,0:18:30.89,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want Noel to disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.52,0:18:32.57,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.37,0:18:42.72,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,So get out of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.18,0:18:49.51,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Does it have to be Togawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.76,0:18:53.16,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay as long as the \Nfive of us aren't together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.77,0:18:56.57,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Then I could just be \Naway from you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.52,0:18:58.70,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.70,0:19:02.87,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I caused so much trouble \Nabout the saucer, so I—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.87,0:19:05.47,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,How could we leave it to \Nyou, Yuzuki, you idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.47,0:19:07.32,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, stupid Souta.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.32,0:19:09.23,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.22,0:19:22.19,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Souta...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.62,0:19:26.15,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Yuzuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.68,0:19:28.22,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.27,0:19:30.44,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.44,0:19:32.23,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Koharu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.59,0:19:33.62,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.94,0:19:35.13,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.80,0:19:40.36,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Did Shione tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.25,0:19:46.51,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.75,0:20:07.47,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.73,0:20:25.37,sora-internal,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I heard your voices in the sky \Nabove the observatory that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.24,0:20:28.04,sora-internal,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Your voices calling for the saucer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.49,0:20:30.06,sora-internal,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Calling for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.44,0:20:33.12,sora-internal,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,That's how I got to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.81,0:20:37.05,sora-internal,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it was you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.79,0:20:40.26,sora-internal,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,as soon as I met you, Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.83,0:20:42.86,sora-internal,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I was so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.95,0:20:49.90,sora-internal,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I spent time with you, and you \Ntaught me a beautiful song.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.73,0:20:55.07,sora-internal,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,And the meals you \Nmade were so tasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.39,0:20:58.89,sora-internal,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuki and Koharu,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.39,0:21:02.31,sora-internal,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Souta and Shione
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.40,0:21:06.82,sora-internal,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,are all so kind and warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.51,0:21:12.85,sora-internal,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I smiled lots and lots.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.97,0:21:17.14,sora-internal,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I know now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.64,0:21:20.09,sora-internal,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,What I want to see
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.05,0:21:23.51,sora-internal,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,is you, Shione,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.71,0:21:25.85,sora-internal,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Koharu, Yuzuki,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.05,0:21:29.72,sora-internal,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,and Souta smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.22,0:21:33.35,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Because I love you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.53,0:21:44.61,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,That's why
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.32,0:21:50.32,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I have to part with you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.63,0:23:34.51,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode of {\i1}Celestial Method{\i0}: \N"Night of the Meteor Shower."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.65,0:23:35.81,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.81,0:23:39.31,sora-next-ep,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Night of the Meteor Shower
